[b][size=150]Compatibility[/size][/b]
Tested and working on Firefox Stable/Dev. Edition, SeaMonkey and Palemoon.
[b][color=#FF0000]Not compatible with Nightly nor Windows Vista[/color][/b]

[b][size=150]Usage[/size][/b]
[list]
[*] Edit this button Initialization tab to change its preferences.
[*] The [b]prefName[/b] variable is the full name of the preference that you want to control with this button.
[*] The [b]switchButtonImage[/b] variable set to true will allow you to change this button image depending on the preference current value.
[*] The [b]boolEnabledImage[/b] and [b]boolDisabledImage[/b] variables are the images used by [b]boolean[/b] preferences.
[*] The [b]prefValues[/b] variable is an array of values for [b]integer[/b] and/or [b]string[/b] preferences. It has to have at least 2 values. Every time this button is clicked, the preference will switch its value between the values defined here.
[*] The [b]prefImages[/b] variable is an array of links to images for [b]integer[/b] and/or [b]string[/b] preferences. The first image in this variable correspond to the first value in the [b]prefValues[/b] variable. The second image, to the second value in the [b]prefValues[/b] variable, and so forth.
[*] This button can be cloned/installed countless times to control/switch any preference of any type.[/list]

[b][size=150]Button clicks[/size][/b]
[list]
[*] [b]Left click:[/b] Switch preference.
[*] [b]Shift + Left click:[/b] Switch preference (Inverse).
[*] [b]Middle click[/b] or [b]Control/Command + Left click:[/b] Set preference prompt.[/list]

